	   Jan. 20: Comedian Arte Johnson is 66. Movie director David Lynch is 54.
Musician Ian Hill of Judas Priest is 48. Comedian Bill Maher is 44. Actor
Lorenzo Lamas is 42. Actress Stacey Dash ("Clueless") is 33. Singer Xavier is
32.
